questionsAndAnswers.question: What details do you need to get started with the project
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will need Wix login details, business logo, text, images, and the type of web pages or if you have any Figma  Design files.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website after its developed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, definitely. You can easily edit your site. I will give you basic knowledge for web designing so that you can easily maintain your website. Anytime you require assistance I will be there for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Support after completion of project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, i will help you out with every possible thing after the completion of the project as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have Figma website .can you convert it, Figma to wix ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: YES,,I  will do Figma to Wix. please provide your Figma website link or file.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work on Wix Studio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I work on Wix Studio and am well-versed in all its advanced features, making sure you get a high-quality, customized site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you redesign my existing website to make it more modern and professional?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Definitely! I specialize in giving outdated websites a fresh, modern look while optimizing functionality and user experience.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide SEO optimization for my Wix website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I include basic SEO setup for your website, such as optimizing titles, descriptions, and keywords. For more advanced SEO, I offer dedicated SEO services to boost your site’s visibility.
